;Quick Filter Toolbar
Kikajtz'ik taq rusamajib'al aninäq taq chayub'äl


;The Quick Filter Toolbar lets you filter your email faster. Start typing in words in the Quick Filter search box and the results are displayed instantly. Or you can filter your email by New Messages, Tags, and people in your Address Book. You can also "Pin" or save a Filter and use it across multiple folders.
Ri kiyuqtz'ik taq rusamajib'al Aninäq Chayunïk nuya' q'ij chawe ye'achayuj chanin ri taq ataqoya'l. Tatikirisaj ye'atz'ib'aj taq tzij pa ri rukanob'al Aninäq chayunïk pa aninäq yeb'echolajitäj pe. Chuqa' yatikïr ye'achayuj ri taq taqoya'l ruma K'ak'a' taq Rutzijol, taq Etal chuqa' ri winaqi' e k'o pa ochochib'äl tz'ib'awuj. Chuqa' yatikïr "Pin" o nayäq jun chayub'äl richin nawokisaj kik'in jalajöj taq cholyakb'äl.


;Search
Tikanöx


;The search interface in Thunderbird contains filtering and timeline tools to pinpoint the exact email you’re looking for. Thunderbird also indexes all of your emails to help you search even faster. Your search results are displayed in a tab so you can easily switch back and forth to your search results and other email.
Ri ruk'amal kanob'äl pa Thunderbird ruk'wan taq rusamajib'al chayunïk chuqa' ruk'amaya'l q'ijul richin niya' retal ri qitzij taqoya'l tajin nakanoj. Thunderbird yenuk' konojel ri taq ataqoya'l richin yatruto' aninäq rik'in jun kanoxïk. Ri aq'i'oj richin kanoxïk xkek'ut pe pa jun ruwi' richin yatikïr aninäq najalwachij chi rij o chuwäch ri taq q'i'oj xe'ilitäj chuqa' ri ch'aqa' chik taq taqoya'l.


;Message Archive
Tiyakb'ëx Rutzijol


;If you think you’re going to need an email in the future but want it out of your inbox without deleting it, archive it! Archiving helps you manage your inbox and put your email into the archive folder system.
