;Robust Privacy
Kowiläj Ichinanem


;Thunderbird offers support for user privacy and remote image protection. To ensure a user’s privacy, Thunderbird automatically blocks remote images in email messages.
Thunderbird nusüj to'ïk richin ri richinanem qawinaq chuqa' kichajinïk näj taq wachib'äl. Richin nijikib'äl richinanem qawinaq, Thunderbird pa ruyonil yeruq'ät näj taq wachib'äl pa taq rutzijol taqoya'l.


;Phishing Protection
Chajinïk chuwäch K'exonel


;Thunderbird protects you from email scams which try to trick users into handing over personal and confidential information by indicating when a message is a potential phishing attempt. As a second line of defense, Thunderbird warns you when you click on a link which appears to be taking you to a different Web site than the one indicated by the URL in the message.
Thuderbird yatruchajij chuwäch eläq' pa taqoya'l, ri nitojtob'ej yekiq'öl ri taq qawinaq richin nikijäch ketamab'al toq jun rutzijol kan jun rutojtob'enïk k'exonel. Achi'el jun ruka'n rutzijol kolïk, Thunderbird nuya' rutzijol chawe jampe' k'o chi napïtz' pa ruwi' jun ximonel, ri achi'el ta chi yatruk'waj pa jun chik wi chi ruxaq k'amaya'l man achi'el ta ri nuk'üt ri rochochib'al URL richin ri rutzijol.


;Automated Update
Taq k'exoj pa kiyonil


;Thunderbird’s update system checks to see if you’re running the latest version, and notifies you when a security update is available. These security updates are small (usually 200KB - 700KB), giving you only what you need and making the security update quick to download and install. The automated update system provides updates for Thunderbird on Windows, Mac OS X, and Linux in over 40 different languages.
Ri kiq'inoj taq ruk'exoj Thunderbird nunik'oj we tajin nib'anatäj ri ruk'isib'äl ruwäch, chuqa' nuya' rutzijol chawe toq k'o jun ruk'exoj jikomal. Re taq kik'exoj jikomal re' e koköj ok (junelïk 200KB - 700KB) ri nikiya' chawe xa xe ri nik'atzin chawe rik'in ri' nikib'än chi re ri ruk'exoj jikomal aninäq richin naqasäx kan chuqa' niyak qa. Ri kiq'inoj yonil taq k'exoj nikiya' taq k'exoj richin Thunderbird pa Windows, Mac OS X chuqa' Linux pa jotöl chi re ri 40 jalajöj taq ch'ab'äl.


;Cutting Out the Junk
Taqupij ri seq'


;Thunderbird’s popular junk mail tools have been updated to stay ahead of spam. Each email you receive passes through Thunderbird’s leading-edge junk mail filters. Each time you mark messages as spam, Thunderbird "learns" and improves its filtering so you can spend more time reading the mail that matters. Thunderbird can also use your mail provider’s spam filters to keep junk mail out of your inbox.
Ri ajtz'etel taq rusamajib'al seq' taqoya'l richin Thunderbird, xk'ex richin nik'oje' chuwäch ri seq'tz'ijol. Chi jujun ri taq taqoya'l xe'ak'ül yeq'ax pa jun nima'q taq chayub'äl richin seq' taqoya'l richin Thunderbird. Toq naya' retal jun rutzijol chi seq'tzijol, Thunderbird "nretamaj" chuqa' nurutzilaj ri chayunïk richin chi naya' k'ïy ruq'ijul ye'asik'ij ri nimaläj taq taqoya'l. Thunderbird chuqa' nitikïr yerokisaj ri taq ruchayub'al seq'tzijol richin ri aya'öl taqoya'l richin man yek'oje' ta ri taq seq' taqoya'l pa taqob'äl.


